(1541, 1, '2013-11-13 20:42:01', '2013-11-13 20:42:01', '[two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n\r\n[elements_animation animation_type=''element_from_left'']\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1145" alt="process-01" src="http://www.skygatemedia.com/clients.hold/lifesports/V3/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/LifeSports-01.jpg" width="487" height="325" />\r\n\r\n[/elements_animation]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n[two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''15'' down=''15'']\r\n<h4>LIFESPORTS: A REGIONAL DESTINATION</h4>\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''5'' down=''5'']\r\n\r\nLifeSports will be a new hybrid of a Youth Sports Complex that will include corporate showcases and specialty retailers targeting the active and health conscience consumer. Leveraging your brand, we will create a regional sports destination, we will attract youth and adult athletes with competitive national and league tournaments.\r\n\r\nLifeSports will become the new business model for the recreational sports center industry:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Leverage the your brand with a location based sports concept</li>\r\n	<li>Centers in all major US markets: sites selected for New York and Miami</li>\r\n	<li>Maximize income from specialty retail, corporate partnerships and food service</li>\r\n	<li>Target the health and active life style demographic</li>\r\n	<li>Year-round generation of sports content for broadcast and digital programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''25'' down=''25'']\r\n\r\n[two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''15'' down=''15'']\r\n<h4>Core Audience</h4>\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''5'' down=''5'']\r\n\r\nThe three primary target audiences for LifeSports are the following:\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Destination field sports participants:</strong></h4>\r\n\r\nThe core of LifeSports'' target audience are players and supporters of youth and adult field sports. These are scheduled events {practices, training and games} that, depending upon the teams, attract\r\neither a family or young adult audience.\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n[two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[elements_animation animation_type=''element_from_right'']\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-1146 alignright" alt="process-02" src="http://www.skygatemedia.com/clients.hold/lifesports/V3/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/LifeSports-02.jpg" width="487" height="325" />\r\n\r\n[/elements_animation]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''25'' down=''25'']\r\n\r\n[two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n\r\n[elements_animation animation_type=''element_from_left'']\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1147" alt="process-03" src="http://www.skygatemedia.com/clients.hold/lifesports/V3/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/LifeSports-03.jpg" width="487" height="325" />\r\n\r\n[/elements_animation]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n[two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''15'' down=''15'']\r\n<h4>Moms:</h4>\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''5'' down=''5'']\r\n\r\nOur goal is to extend the length of stay of Moms who may initially visit LifeSports as part of their child''s field sports program. We want to develop programming to create opportunities to capture Moms and offer family activities. Mom''s are the Family CDO (Chief Decision Officer).\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''25'' down=''25'']\r\n\r\n[two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''15'' down=''15'']\r\n<h4>Regional and national sports event participants</h4>\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''5'' down=''5'']\r\n\r\nLifeSports will be the regiona