rds, and use them as your key to lockers, equipment rooms and other special access areas)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/unordered_list]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''25'' down=''25'']\r\n\r\n[two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n\r\n[separator type=''transparent'' color='''' thickness='''' up=''15'' down=''15'']\r\n<h4 style="font-weight: 500;">GUEST AMENITIES</h4>\r\n[unordered_list style=''circle'' animate=''no'']\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Culinary excellence: A wide range of food and beverage options, from a fresh fruit and smoothie bar to a sports-themed cafe, all with a focus on healthy eating and nutritional education</li>\r\n	<li>Retail area: An ancillary retail section focusing exclusively on sports, health and nutrition, including a vitamin store, organic produce and sporting goods</li>\r\n	<li>Health and wellness: An on-site sports medicine and wellness center, weight loss clinic, nail and hair salon</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/unordered_list]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col1]\r\n[two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n[elements_animation animation_type=''element_from_right'']\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-1150 alignright" alt="GUEST AMENITIES" src="http://www.skygatemedia.com/clients.hold/lifesports/V3/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/LifeSports-GUESTAMENITIES.jpg" width="487" height="325" />\r\n\r\n[/elements_animation]\r\n\r\n[/two_col_50_50_col2]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About LifeSports USA', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1095-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-21 02:55:28', '2013-11-21 02:55:28', '', 1095, 'http://www.skygatemedia.com/clients.hold/lifesports/V3/2013/11/21/1095-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
